                    <p>
                        <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:ddanda">.</g></supplied> matirai koṇṭa kopparakecaripaṉma<unclear>ṟ</unclear>ku yāṇṭu Irupattoṉpatāvatu tiruveṅkaṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ṅkai <unclear>ca</unclear>ṅkara<unclear>ṉ raṇa</unclear>ciṅkaṉākiya <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/>
                        <lb n="2"/>kku Oṉṟiṉukkut tiruveṅkaṭak koṭṭattu kuṭavūr nāṭṭu tiruccoru<unclear>ṉū</unclear>r <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Ipponṉiṟ palicaiyiṉāl nicati pa <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> 
