                        <lb n="3"/><unclear>kkoru tiru</unclear>n<unclear>o<!--kompu clear--></unclear>ntāviḷakkiṉukku Oṉṟarai mañcāṭikku pūrattukku pa <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
