                <p n="B5">In continuation of this piece another inscription seems to begin with <foreign>matiraiko</foreign>. There is also another piece containing the following two lines in characters of about the 11th century A.D. 
                    <foreign><lb n="1"/> pakkal <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yom viṟṟukkoṇṭu Uṭaiya 
